			<h3 class="date">Monday, March 28, 2011</h3>			
<div class="post post-6028 hentry clearfix  category-uncategorized">
	<div class="slugs"><a title="fashion" href="http://thehairpin.com/slug/fashion">fashion</a></div>
	<a class="comments" href="http://thehairpin.com/2011/03/man-cannot-remove-his-tiny-hat#comments">30</a>
	<h2><a title="Man Cannot Remove His Tiny Hat" href="http://thehairpin.com/2011/03/man-cannot-remove-his-tiny-hat">Man Cannot Remove His Tiny Hat</a></h2>
	<div class="byline">
		By <a title="Edith Zimmerman" href="http://thehairpin.com/user/2/edith">Edith Zimmerman</a>		<a class="time" href="http://thehairpin.com/2011/03/man-cannot-remove-his-tiny-hat">| March 28, 2011</a>
	</div>
	<div class="entry entry-content">
		<p><iframe title="YouTube video player" width="640" height="390" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/eK1EPP6uts0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>Shawn has superglued a miniature sequined fedora to the side of his head, and what was fashionable by night has become a living nightmare by day.</p>

<p>In related news, Dr. Harry Coover, the creator of Super Glue, <a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-12879603">has passed away</a> at the age of 94.</p>	</div><!-- .entry -->
	
		
</div><!-- .post -->

